## CUSTOM-CONF: File automatically created/updated [custom-conf-libvirt]


## LibVirt daemon settings

# Start daemon:
start_libvirtd="yes"

# Daemon options
libvirtd_opts="%{CUSTOM_CONF_LIBVIRT_DAEMON_OPTIONS}"

# Kerberos keytab
KRB5_KTNAME=/etc/krb5.keytab

# Control groups (cgroups)
# (assume systemd is running and managing those)

